{"tid":2041110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向橋下掟磚助築路障 被指險擊中警員 澳洲女子認企圖襲警囚三個月","createTime":"2020-05-29T04:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T06:37:34.000Z","uid":242903,"like":34,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"248ea30faf08d2e2b8c86078510e66e98ad0ff4b","tid":2041110,"uid":242903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"去年11月12日「破曉行動」三罷當日，澳洲籍女插畫師在中環行人天橋向下掟磚，協助示威者築路障，當時馬路上有一批警員正在推進。她早前在東區裁判法院承認企圖襲警罪。裁判官香淑嫻今斥責被告所作行為嚴重危害前線警務人員的安全，判她即時監禁三個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200529/GFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FGFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33PUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=77790035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FGFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=da6c9822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200529/GFYO25PHQ5WY7A7BUZKH2ASRKE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n勿忘手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f666814cb8f6d262fb2675809fc2c6d322bcb9","tid":2041110,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947dcc855b39fc898249dfc9f2bee397124a1f46","tid":2041110,"uid":28195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"3kg k仔就無事"},{"pid":"8649565208530